WEBVTT

00:02:57.351 --> 00:03:00.221
Ali ignorisali smo Kuznetsovo upozorenje.

00:03:00.221 --> 00:03:01.777
Živimo u svetu u kome je

00:03:01.777 --> 00:03:04.900
BDP standard uspeha

00:03:04.900 --> 00:03:07.177
u globalnoj ekonomiji.

00:03:07.177 --> 00:03:10.406
Naši političari se hvale kada BDP poraste.

00:03:10.406 --> 00:03:11.690
Tržišta se kreću

00:03:11.690 --> 00:03:13.564
i bilioni dolara kapitala

00:03:13.564 --> 00:03:14.988
kruže svetom

00:03:14.988 --> 00:03:16.739
na osnovu porasta

00:03:16.739 --> 00:03:18.580
i pada određenih zemalja,

00:03:18.580 --> 00:03:21.204
u merenju BDP-a.

00:03:21.204 --> 00:03:22.853
Naša društva su postala

00:03:22.853 --> 00:03:26.908
mašine za stvaranje većeg BDP-a.

00:03:26.908 --> 00:03:30.443
Ali znamo da BDP ima mana.